### ğŸ§  Step 3: **Backend Processes the Request (à¦¬à§à¦¯à¦¾à¦•à¦à¦¨à§à¦¡ à¦•à¦¾à¦œ à¦•à¦°à§‡)**

* Backend checks the route (e.g., `/login`)
